query_my_light
Discworld object help
query_my_light

Name
.SI 5
query_my_light - Returns the light level of just the object.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
int query_my_light();
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
Returns just the lumenosity of the object itself.  Not includeing the
light levels of any object inside it or that are affecting it in some
way.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
set_light, query_light, light, query_int_light
.EP
